A variation of [url=https://www.shadertoy.com/view/ldy3D1]Liquid stuff 2[/url]...

Controls:
- Mouse: draw colliders;
- Mouse + SPACE: erase colliders;
- LEFT / RIGHT: rotate the gravity;
- DOWN: invert the gravity;
- R: reset the scene.

